-- Banca Leonardo Hires Wallendahl, Plans Firm's Expansion in Northern Europe
-- Elisa Martinuzzi
-- 2010-07-07T10:31:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/banca-leonardo-hires-wallendahl-plans-firm-s-expansion-in-northern-europe.html

          
          
             Gruppo Banca Leonardo SpA said it
hired Berent Wallendahl as chairman of its European Advisory
Operating Committee.  
 Wallendahl, who will oversee the German market, will also
be responsible for expanding the firm in northern Europe,
Switzerland and Austria, according to an e-mailed statement
today.  
          
          


  


        